# Define variables
@base_url=https://httpbin.org
@token=my-secret-token

### GET request with variable interpolation
GET {{base_url}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### POST request with a body
POST {{base_url}}/post
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Alice", "email": "alice@example.com"}
